column4: This is the Nick Richards I Know 💯💯 Keep Killing my brother don’t let ya foot off the gas ! @iamnickrichards

Bittersweet news out of @PSAhoops loss: Hassan Diarra passes Hamidou Diallo to become #PSAHoops all-time leading scorer w 1,435 points. Milestone hoop on a FT midway thru 2nd half. It’s not sexy but it did the job...Congratulations @hassan_diarra11! 
@hamidoudiallo @aggiembk https://t.co/BsLTyiGfiJ
Eid Mubarak to all my muslim brothers and sisters. May Allah accept our fasting and our prayers and forgive our transgressions and bring peace to all suffering 🙏🏾🖤🤞🏾
